name: Sessão / #5 - Mushroom sofa
description:
The session is in the air and someone climbed the mushroom to escape the water, at least it seems to be comfortable and have a great view.

Fifth piece of the “Sessão” collection.

*The collection entitled "Sessão" brings together six different illustrations previously produced, taking the troop of intergalactic friends to a classic session around Cogulândia, a magical and hallucinating world.
